keyFacts: The FBI's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk in New York is involved in issuing or collecting subpoenas related to American Airlines.
Two separate subpoenas to American Airlines are referenced, dated January 23, 2020, and June 29, 2021, from two different cases.
The communication indicates ongoing investigative activity involving airline records, potentially related to travel patterns in exploitation cases.
